snippet.title: Fire Commander Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase
snippet.description:
Take control of a team of firefighters where you have to manage the extreme heat, environment and saving civilians. 

In this trailer we get to experience the pressure firefighters are under, gameplay and where you can play it when it comes out. 

#FireCommander
